  &lt;option value="4"&gt;Dedicated resources for core data management functions&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="5"&gt;Comprehensive resource allocation across all data management dimensions&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;
How does your organization invest in data management technology and tools?
&lt;select class="form-select"&gt;
