  &lt;option value="3"&gt;Planned investment in core data management technologies&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="4"&gt;Strategic investment in integrated data management technologies&lt;/option&gt;
  &lt;option value="5"&gt;Continuous investment in advanced data capabilities and innovation&lt;/option&gt;
&lt;/select&gt;



Risk Management

How does your organization identify and manage data-related risks?
&lt;select class="form-select"&gt;
  &lt;option value="" selected disabled&gt;Please select...&lt;/option&gt;
